{"tid":1486563,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"好欣賞香港人既黑色幽默|苦中作樂","createTime":"2019-08-19T02:07:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-19T08:27:45.000Z","uid":193485,"like":89,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"66afd56d382f01ad1cce6dccbcdb0eee6cc7de06","tid":1486563,"uid":193485,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T02:07:29.000Z","msg":"1. 工聯會外放菠蘿，表揚支聯暴徒六七暴動<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OmNsHJ4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOmNsHJ4.jpg&h=72888ea9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n2. 與支持福獨既內地同胞留影，簡直係血濃於水<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NAK6YhL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNAK6YhL.jpg&h=e22195ba&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n3. 一眾太空戰士聲援方仲賢，勁歌熱舞「激光中」<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/Fe7wQbWkJHo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FFe7wQbWkJHo&d=L%2B62T2%2Bn9M6BECqB4mLSsq0IH4hhGWFtD%2BQErH2Rjq0%3D&h=88ad2cc6\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/Fe7wQbWkJHo</a><br />\n<br />\n4. 向甲甴行使最低武力，維護社會秩序<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/p/B1TsLjGgGTV/?igshid=iq81lq3aat3e\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FB1TsLjGgGTV%2F%3Figshid%3Diq81lq3aat3e&d=L%2B62T2%2Bn9M6BECqB4mLSsq0IH4hhGWFtD%2BQErH2Rjq0%3D&h=c9c86396\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FB1TsLjGgGTV%2F%3Figshid%3Diq81lq3aat3e&h=2e354045\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/p/B1TsLjGgGTV/?igshid=iq81lq3aat3e</a><br />\n<br />\n5. 超幽佈施祈福除惡晚會，齊心驅散超渡邪警<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/p/B08eecGgXPI/?igshid=1impk5nx7pmv2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FB08eecGgXPI%2F%3Figshid%3D1impk5nx7pmv2&d=L%2B62T2%2Bn9M6BECqB4mLSsq0IH4hhGWFtD%2BQErH2Rjq0%3D&h=f6d06183\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FB08eecGgXPI%2F%3Figshid%3D1impk5nx7pmv2&h=2bfdcf97\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/p/B08eecGgXPI/?igshid=1impk5nx7pmv2</a><br />\n<br />\n兩個多月，一路走來，發生咗好多天怒人怨既事<br />\n所幸是即使面對邪惡極權，港人並冇退縮放棄，<br />\n一方面以更大既怒火反擊政權，另一方面以黑色幽默苦中作樂。<br />\n<br />\n請大家謹記，<br />\n黎明前既黑夜就係最撚黑暗，但無論係幾撚黑暗，我地都唔可以絕望、唔可以放棄，唔可以辜負同路人、義士、同嗰6位烈士。<br />\n<br />\n革命尚未成功，還請大家切勿鬆懈。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n因果由國，容港治己。<br />\n光復香港，時代革命。<br />\n五大訴求，缺一不可。<br />\n<br />\n不成功，便成仁。<br />\n<br />\n831見。<br />\n</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">一邊打一邊流馬尿，能夠同大家一齊抗爭實在係我既榮幸，多謝你地。<br />\nProud to be Hongkonger</span>"},{"pid":"5c273841aed5dc983999c1bd1db6ec738ac6b6ec","tid":1486563,"uid":276783,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T02:09:00.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b379905cadca63455b02ad9c85dea2bf4c74c85a","tid":1486563,"uid":276783,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T02:09:25.000Z","msg":"多謝咁多位 真心香港既香港人<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"295e6593cd72f7c30d1198bf1d41f8f9e0c48d53","tid":1486563,"uid":193485,"like":16,"dislike":2,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T02:15:25.000Z","msg":"題外話 小弟由上高登到連登 一直都唔敢俾其他人知自己有上<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n廢事人地覺得我係痴線佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n然後俾女朋友發現我有上連登之後 佢勁唔中意 話會睇壞腦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />成日都要收收埋埋咁上<br />\n依家，連我女友都down咗連登<br />\n我終於可以光明正大咁同人講<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我係連登仔呀Hi<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/